```{r}
cv19 <- read.csv("COVID-19_Case_Surveillance_Public_Use_Data.csv")

                      col_types = cols(pos_spec_dt = col_date(format="")))

test_data <- cv19_tidy[,1]
test_data$cdc_report_dt %<>% factor()
levels(test_data$cdc_report_dt) <- seq(1, 286, by=1)
levels(test_data$cdc_report_dt)
tabl <- as.data.frame(table(test_data$cdc_report_dt))
```

```{r}
mod <- glm(Var1~Freq, data=tabl, family="poisson")
```
